<paragraph blockId="32.[1396,2602,2302,3040]" pageId="32" pageNumber="311">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1396,1634,2810,2843]" pageId="32" pageNumber="311">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The Black-eared Red-backed Vole has relatively low body temperature (35-8°C) and proportionally high basal metabolic rate.
</paragraph>
